UNITED STATES of America, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. Ignacia DIAZ-ESPINDOLA, Defendant-Appellant. No. 89-30321. United States Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Filed June 11, 1991.

Before Procter Hug, Jr. and Dorothy W. Nelson, Circuit Judges, and Vaughn R. Walker *, District Judge.

The Honorable Vaughn R. Walker, United States District Judge for the Northern District of California, sitting by designation.

ORDER

The opinion filed March 14, 1991 is hereby withdrawn. A Memorandum disposition will be filed in its place.
